                    "You've completed {stats.completedUnits} units. Focusing on <span className="text-blue-400 font-bold">{stats.needFocusSubject?.name}</span> for the next 14 days will optimize your overall Batch Index most efficiently."
                   </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="glass-card rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border-emerald-500/10 bg-emerald-500/5">
